==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Promptitude
<hw>Prompt"i*tude</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. L.
<ets>promptitudo</ets>. See <er>Prompt</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety>
<def>The quality of being prompt; quickness of decision and action when
occasion demands; alacrity; <as>as, <ex>promptitude</ex> in
obedience</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Men of action, of <qex>promptitude</qex>, and of courage.</q>
<rj><qau>I. Taylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Promptly</ent>⟦br⟧
